  "id": "named_jars_are_isolated",
  "description": "Named jars are isolated from each other and from the default jar (spec \u00a73.3, \u00a715.6). Call 0 sets sid=admin in jar \"admin\". Call 1 sets sid=user in jar \"user\". Call 2 uses jar \"admin\" \u2014 it sees only sid=admin, not sid=user.",
  "spec_refs": [
    "lace-spec.md \u00a73.3",
    "lace-spec.md \u00a715.6"
  ],
  "type": "execute",
